public class ToDoListDialog
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.DialogBox

This is ToDoList Dialog class. it the dialog that is shown on the screen. it also stores ToDoList objects which stores TaskObjects.Every Task method is in this class.

Creates a new Task on to-do list that this dialog is representing and opens edit screen for new task. if cancel button is pressed on edit screen new task will be deleted.
